---
title: Turkey and Pepper Tacos with Lime Crema and Salsa Fresca
description: A satisfying plate of tacos is just what the doctor ordered! For these handhelds, roasted peppers and onions are paired with seasoned ground turkey, zesty lime crema and a homemade salsa fresca!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-a-la-dinde-et-aux-poivrons-347a6437.jpg
